The paper focuses on improving the performance of search engines through query reformulation using a neural network trained with reinforcement learning. This topic is closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of neural networks and reinforcement learning also suggests potential relevance to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
